Requirements
============

  - pdf(la)tex
  - fourier-GUT, from http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/fonts/fourier-GUT
  - minionpro, see
    http://carlo-hamalainen.net/blog/2007/12/11/installing-minion-pro-fonts/ on Ubuntu
    http://jetdl.com/download/Installation+guide+for+Minion+Pro+and+Myriad+Pro+on+MiKTeX/498h0 on Windows
  - texlive-humanities for bibleref
  - texlive-lang-french for French hyphenation
  - texlive-latex-extra
  - texlive-fonts-extra for MnSymbol needed by MinionPro and fourier-orns


Building and uploading
=======================

Type the following:

   make && make crocupload && make upload

You need two configuration files:

   - ~/.crocodoc.conf with a TOKEN variable with your crocodoc token
   - ~/.ncftp/cc.cfg with the FTP settings

